Miscellaneous
*************

   * *`DFView' is fontsensitiv*

     `DFView' adapts itself completely to the fonts you selected in the
     font preferences program of the Workbench! This means that the
     window will become bigger, if you select a font larger than 8
     points!  If the window becomes too large to fit into the screen,
     `DFView' falls back to a smaller font.

     Please notice that you can change the fonts used by `DFView' via
     the `MUI-Prefs' additionally.

   * *Window Positions*

     `DFView' remembers the positions of all its windows.  This means
     that the windows reopen on the same place you closed them!  Saving
     of the window positions takes place if you save the settings of the
     `MUI-Prefs'.


@EndNode

